<li class="taxonomy_term_49 last"><a href="category/tags/isp.html" rel="tag" title="">isp</a></li>
</ul></div>
    
  </div> <!-- /.node-header -->

  <div class="content">
    
    <p>With the recent instability in Facebook access and some people reporting it blocked on one ISP or area of Vietnam while others can access it just fine... Is it time for you to rethink your choice in internet service provider?</p>
<p>There are a dozen or so ISPs in Vietnam but I've only looked at the biggest: Viettel, VNPT, FPT, SPT, and Netnam.  They also all provide fiber internet (FTTH - fiber to the home) and not just ADSL.  Here are their prices for selected packages:</p>

